32:49.881 --> 32:51.849
Hold on a second.

32:57.188 --> 32:58.856
What?

32:58.890 --> 33:00.090
It's Toby.

33:00.125 --> 33:02.860
He says, cancel everything.
The wedding's off.

33:02.894 --> 33:05.095
Am I allowed to be happy?

