Thank you for coming.

33:08.817 --> 33:10.768
Of course. Is she all
right? What's going on?

33:10.802 --> 33:13.704
Abby's fine. She's napping.

33:13.738 --> 33:15.739
Then why am I here?

33:15.774 --> 33:17.775
Victor couldn't come?

33:17.809 --> 33:20.398
No, it's a three-hour drive, and frankly,

33:20.399 --> 33:21.399
he didn't want me to come either.

33:21.546 --> 33:23.681
I apologize for making you drive that long.

33:23.715 --> 33:25.749
No. We love Abby.

33:25.784 --> 33:27.718
We'll always think of her as ours.

33:27.752 --> 33:30.321
And as much as I want to come running

33:30.355 --> 33:33.457
every time I hear that
she's upset, I can't.

33:33.491 --> 33:35.492
Do you know what an open adoption is?

33:37.429 --> 33:40.130
We can't pop in and out
of her life like that,

33:40.165 --> 33:42.299
just seeing her every now
and then and getting letters.

33:42.334 --> 33:44.335
It's just... it's too hard.

33:54.913 --> 33:57.014
I mean the other way around.

34:06.091 --> 34:08.792
Would you want that?

34:10.094 --> 34:12.663
You know, with my other daughters

34:12.697 --> 34:16.033
we have a mix of biological
and other parents,

34:16.067 --> 34:19.670
and somehow it works.

34:19.704 --> 34:22.473
I think Abby will be better off

34:22.507 --> 34:23.841
with all of us in her life.

34:28.847 --> 34:31.447
Um, how... how would we do it?

34:31.483 --> 34:34.451
I will come every few weekends,

34:34.485 --> 34:36.487
birthdays, summers.

34:36.521 --> 34:38.355
Look, I don't know exactly...

34:39.524 --> 34:41.358
but I'm sure we can find an arrangement

34:41.393 --> 34:43.494
that makes everyone comfortable.

34:43.527 --> 34:45.529
(Chuckles)

34:49.501 --> 34:52.436
Oh, she's gonna have three dads.

34:52.469 --> 34:54.405
Yeah.

35:11.940 --> 35:13.157
You've got a real nice setup here.

35:17.796 --> 35:19.730
You're a lucky girl.

35:31.743 --> 35:33.660
<i>Jace: You want me to post this?</i>

35:33.711 --> 35:35.646
This would expose
Parker's affair with Coto.

35:35.680 --> 35:37.714
<i>Daphne: I got her okay.</i>

35:37.749 --> 35:39.766
You're sure about this?

35:39.818 --> 35:41.585
I could leave your name out of it.

35:41.619 --> 35:44.321
No.

35:44.355 --> 35:46.290
You're not a citizen.

35:46.324 --> 35:49.393
They'll revoke your visa
and you'll be deported.

35:49.427 --> 35:52.646
I'm not gonna let you take a fall for me

35:52.697 --> 35:55.482
when I'm the one who got us into this mess.

35:55.533 --> 35:58.469
We both did it.

35:58.503 --> 36:01.138
I'm just sorry I messed everything up.

36:01.172 --> 36:04.274
I keep telling you, you
weren't the only one.

36:04.309 --> 36:07.211
No, I mean with us.

36:07.245 --> 36:09.463
The first time I saw you

36:09.514 --> 36:12.349
fighting with Bay in sign language,

36:12.383 --> 36:14.318
I was mesmerized by you.

36:14.352 --> 36:16.987
What are you talking about?

36:17.021 --> 36:19.122
You were so mean to me after that.

36:19.157 --> 36:21.008
And it totally worked.

36:30.835 --> 36:33.187
We should have stuck to geocaching.

36:38.910 --> 36:42.746
So would you like to do the honors?

36:52.724 --> 36:55.492
- (Beeps)
- It's done.

37:04.886 --> 37:07.771
- M.B., what's up?
- What's the matter with you?

37:09.757 --> 37:12.659
