now and get on with her life.

38:18.076 --> 38:19.059
You can't tell her.

38:21.796 --> 38:23.714
Don't make me keep this from her.

38:23.765 --> 38:25.766
You have to, all right?

38:25.800 --> 38:27.096
I promised your brother

38:27.107 --> 38:28.662
